r two years later, having noted her perseverance and ability to focus in competition.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9620569234417741, \"rank\": 0.02316447130399059, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.315628620328687e-13, \"text\": \"Guangdong\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a local club\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"her perseverance\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"ability\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, Zheng became the youngest athlete to compete at China's National Games where she took the 14th place.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.62824880809015, \"rank\": 0.3927817432796943, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}, {\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9909772567696542, \"rank\": 0.009100915798335732, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the youngest athlete\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"the 14th place\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, she started competing globally in world series and eventually qualified for Paris in Budapest after scoring a successful 540 flip - a difficult routine she tried for the first time in a competition.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995965677858, \"rank\": 4.034324059876766e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999983633643, \"rank\": 1.5652412970910838e-09, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world series\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful 540 flip\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficult routine\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"a competition\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel I am really kicking ass when I skateboard.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ass\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel a bit narcissistic,\\\" Zheng said with a grin in an interview with CCTV.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.62824880809015, \"rank\": 0.3927817432796943, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}, {\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Central_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999996083657464, \"rank\": 3.916343946059854e-07, \"text\": \"CCTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Central_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Central_Television\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a grin\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The skinny girl with a pony tail, who just graduated from primary school a couple of weeks ago, will join a number of teenagers in the women's park event that takes place on Aug. 6, in one of the youngest sports Paris has to offer.\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995965677858, \"rank\": 4.034324059876766e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The skinny girl\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"a pony tail\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"primary school\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"teenagers\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's park event\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1658}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngest sports\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's also among a new generation of Chinese athletes that has defied the stereotype of the country's hardworking, well-disciplined sports people who ordinarily have to spend years to rise up the ranks in the rigorous state-funded training system.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9410487515638284, \"rank\": 0.06263861244391188,